  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients over 19 years old

          -  bowel resection surgery

          -  incision is 3cm or larger

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosed with a connective tissue disease (e.g. Systemic lupus, scleroderma,
             polymyositis, dermatomyositis, Marfan syndrome, Ehler's Danlos, etc.)

          -  The site of planned surgery has a previous surgical scar.
      </textblock>
